      <h2 id="ethos-heading">What we stand on</h2>
      <p><strong>Regeneration over extraction.</strong> Soil is not a growing medium to be used up; it is an ecosystem to be fed. Every service we offer rebuilds the system that keeps working after we leave.</p>
      <p><strong>Food sovereignty.</strong> The more food a community can grow in its own soil, the more resilient it is. That is why we teach — in gardens, at schools, and on every consultation.</p>
      <p><strong>Measure, then act.</strong> We test before we treat. Programs are built on what your soil actually shows, not on what a product label promises.</p>
